law.history: Repealed 2014 Ky. Acts ch. 22, sec. 26, effective July 15, 2014. -- Created 2013 Ky. Acts ch. 121, sec. 36, effective June 25, 2013.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Business authorized by transporter's license -- Transportation of distilled spirits, wine, and malt beverages -- Entities eligible for license -- Reports to Department of Revenue -- Restrictions upon routes traveled -- Examination of cargo -- Illegal trafficking -- Exemption from KRS 243.100 and 244.090.
